nodes.bodyText:
Could we make sure to name the operation here? Additionally, using variables is a best practice, along with identifying your client traffic using the apollographql-client-name header.
Maybe something like this?
query DownloadSchema($graphID: ID!, $variant: String! = "current") {
  service(id: $graphID) {
    variant(name: $variant) {
      activeSchemaPublish {
        schema {
          document
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

